name: Iron Maiden
skill: Deals 3734/4454 DMG to the enemy with the highest ATK. Targets deal 30%/36% less DMG for a limited time.
ability: Skill attacks sharply decrease target's ATK speed.

additional_data.description: The spirit of a torture device that skewers its victims. She likes to boast that the face of the Virgin Mary emblazoned on the device makes her especially kind and loving, and she does manage to bring jobs to a close in a peaceful manner—most of the time, at least. No matter how evil the villain, she gives them a warm embrace and begs them to surrender...not so different from the Virgin Mary, in fact. There used to be rumors that she stabbed those she held with spikes, but one day, the rumors suddenly stopped. The ones who'd experienced her embrace were the first to deny the rumors, almost as if they were scared of something...
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Summon rate increased until 16/08/2017
◦ She was previously renamed Ira Maiden but returned to her original name a few days later.

skill: "Calm down, it'll be over before you know it~♪"
summon: "'Why can't we all just get along?' That's my motto!"
